  <!-- WHO WE ARE -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight mb-6 text-[#0d1b3e] text-center">
        Who <span class="font-semibold text-[#f5c518]">We Are</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-balance">
        Pathways is an initiative under RISE Ubuntu — providing education, mentorship, and community development programmes to equip Zambians for life and leadership.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight mb-6 text-[#0d1b3e] text-center">
        Overview
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-balance">
        Pathways was created to address a fundamental gap: young people in Zambia who are capable and motivated but lack access to structured learning, mentorship, and opportunity. Operating under RISE Ubuntu, Pathways delivers two core programme streams — Education Pathways and Community Pathways. Every programme is designed around the belief that young people, given the right environment and support, will build a stronger Zambia.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VISION & MISSION -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0d1b3e]/5 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0d1b3e] mb-3">Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            “A Zambia where every young person – regardless of background — has access to the knowledge, skills, and networks needed to lead a purposeful, productive life and contribute meaningfully to their community and nation.”
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#0d1b3e]/5 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0d1b3e] mb-3">Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            “To develop students into responsible, capable leaders. To provide structured education, mentorship, and community engagement opportunities.”
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

