  <!-- ABOUT RISE UBUNTU (summary + link) -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight mb-4 text-[#0d1b3e]">
        About <span class="font-semibold text-[#f5c518]">RISE Ubuntu</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-balance mb-6">
        RISE Ubuntu is an emerging social impact organisation currently undergoing formal NGO registration to be based in Zambia, dedicated to the holistic development of young people and communities. "Ubuntu", the African philosophy of shared humanity, sits at the heart of everything the organisation does.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-balance mb-8">
        Through Pathways and other initiatives to come, RISE Ubuntu invests in education, leadership, and social enterprise as pathways out of poverty and into purpose. The organisation works in partnership with government, civil society, and the private sector to maximise reach and impact.
      </p>
      <a href="rise-ubuntu.php" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#f5c518] text-[#0d1b3e] hover:bg-[#f5c518]/90 font-semibold rounded-full px-8 h-12 text-sm group shadow-lg">
        Learn more about RISE Ubuntu
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

